== About me 
One and half years of research experience in Federated Learning projects with AIRS, CUHKSZ, Yale, IBM Research, and WeBank, including optimization, system prototype development, multi-robot collaborative learning, and incentive mechanism design.
Four years of working experience in China Mobile Headquarters as a project manager, leading several projects with Huawei, ZTE, Ericsson, and Nokia in improving the quality of China Mobile wireless network.
Three years completing a Ph.D. degree from Melbourne University, earning three prestigious scholarships.

